&lt;h4 id=&#34;set-the-env&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#set-the-env&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; SET THE ENV&lt;/h4&gt;
